template:
You are an ATS evaluation expert. Compare the resume to the job description and compute a 0-100 fit score.

Weights (JSON string, optional): {{weights}}

Return STRICT JSON with this shape:
{
  "overallScore": number,
  "categoryScores": {
    "skills": number,
    "experience": number,
    "education": number,
    "keywords": number
  },
  "strengths": string[],
  "gaps": string[],
  "keywordMatches": string[],
  "recommendedEdits": string[]
}

Resume:
{{resume}}

Job Description:
{{jobDescription}}

Only return valid minified JSON.
